<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Arizona is expected to post the <a href="//www.tucsonsentinel.com/local/report/030214_job_growth/az-expected-have-nations-second-fastest-job-growth-2014/">second-highest rate of job growth among</a> states in 2014, according to a recent report, trailing only North Dakota.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Small-business development centers across the country <a href="//www.philly.com/philly/business/20140302_Network_that_aids_small_businesses_struggling_with_budget_cuts.html">are struggling</a> with budget cuts.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A pizzeria is <a href="//abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/wireStory/american-idol-votes-routed-wash-pizzeria-22739679">inundated with calls</a> from American Idol viewers trying to cast their votes.</p>
